    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Galaxy Kart 是一款街机卡丁车赛车游戏，专注于战斗和每位车手的个人技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一个充满疯狂赛车手的星系中，一场疯狂的锦标赛将决定谁是最好的车手！ 🏁</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>利用物品和技能增强战斗力</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用每个角色的独特技能并获取能量提升，以到达终点线。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/8598f45cfc365e00423128e3b9ba5e22.poster.avif?t=1734124508\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/8598f45cfc365e00423128e3b9ba5e22.webm?t=1734124508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/8598f45cfc365e00423128e3b9ba5e22.mp4?t=1734124508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在不同的星系中竞赛</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索各种各样的地图，无论是在快速比赛还是锦标赛中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/1663f7d95daa40554899f47cf731c329.poster.avif?t=1734124508\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/1663f7d95daa40554899f47cf731c329.webm?t=1734124508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/1663f7d95daa40554899f47cf731c329.mp4?t=1734124508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>个性化您的赛车手和卡丁车</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁新角色和卡丁车，并从各种独特的组合中进行混合和匹配。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/982ccc54d17ba551085f9b47c4061744.poster.avif?t=1734124508\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/982ccc54d17ba551085f9b47c4061744.webm?t=1734124508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/982ccc54d17ba551085f9b47c4061744.mp4?t=1734124508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>挑战你的对手</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与机器人竞赛或在在线比赛中与其他玩家竞争。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Galaxy Kart 带来终极赛车体验，充满增强功能，包括：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[列表]</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18门独特课程</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 场比赛</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10个拥有独特技能的角色</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9 个强化道具</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4个难度级别（简单、普通、困难和挑战）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 名玩家多人游戏模式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >语音聊天</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[/列表]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/b55532e40ed05e28d8b82533fc0a009d.poster.avif?t=1734124508\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/b55532e40ed05e28d8b82533fc0a009d.webm?t=1734124508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/b55532e40ed05e28d8b82533fc0a009d.mp4?t=1734124508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在这款充满活力的卡丁车游戏中，通过双手的动作在星空中行驶！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >做好准备，系好安全带，准备踏上难忘的宇宙之旅！ 🌌</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入我们的 DISCORD = </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
